sentences: Vitale started his professional music career with The Chylds in 1965 at age 17, and sang vocals on their hit single "I Want More (Lovinâ€™)."The band recorded a number of 45 singles at Akron Recording Studios in Akron, Ohio, at Cleveland Recording and at Gateway in Pittsburgh.
The band broke up in 1968 because some of the band members got married and needed to find jobs to support a family.
Their recording of "Hay Girl" was released in 1984 on the compilation LP Highs in the Mid-Sixties, Volume 9 by AIP Records (as #AIP-10015).
The Chylds were a popular northern Ohio rock band from 1964-68.
